{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"901764dab3","title":"中央军委给新疆军区党委的二封电报","origin":"根据文件的群众组织翻印件，翻印者未注明","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ac629ac247","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":28,"articleId":"901764dab3"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ee21afb82f","name":"新疆文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c125180ef9","type":"title","text":"中央军委给新疆军区党委的二封电报","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"f41f411f9e","type":"subtitle","text":"（一）","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"3eb6e57cfd","type":"paragraph","text":"“绝密","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"6021d1604e","type":"paragraph","text":"新疆军区党委：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"2a804a380a","type":"paragraph","text":"军委认为王恩茂、郭鹏、左齐、张希钦、徐国贤、熊晃、丁盛、裴周玉等八同志的问题是人民内部矛盾，他们不是“三反分子”，不是贺龙分子，望你们向大家作妥善解释。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"a7fc8ce139","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央军委，一九六七年一月二十八日”","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"0c503b9090","type":"subtitle","text":"（二）","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"a4d083937a","type":"paragraph","text":"新疆军区并转全体指战员，革命师生和革命群众：","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"9e0188611a","type":"paragraph","text":"新疆军区对公然违抗毛主席批准的中央军委命令的分子执行纪律是完全正确的。全体指战员、革命师生、革命工人、革命干部都必须支持这个正确措施。希望所有包围新疆军区机关的革命群众都自觉地回到本单位去，向违抗中央军委命令的现象作坚决斗争。否则，一切后果，由冲击新疆军区的人员负完全责任。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"f84d20f090","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央军委1967.2.11","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"07bf1b5a82","type":"paragraph","text":"收机，11日23时50分","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"530d4aae6c","type":"paragraph","text":"译出，12日0时","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"},{"id":"ef68962390","type":"paragraph","text":"打出，12日0时15分","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3"}],"page":{"id":"aa1a93b12d","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"901764dab3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}